
                           ------------------TASK-----------------
create Lottery contract allows players to enter a lottery game by sending 0.1 ether to the contract.
The manager of the contract can then pick a winner at random and transfer the entire balance of the contract to that winner. 
The contract requires a minimum of 3 players to play the lottery.
The contract also keeps track of the players who have entered the lottery and 
allows anyone to view the current list of players.

